    <h3>Variants</h3>

    <p><em>Compact</em> and <em>Extended</em> are the two promo banner variants. Compact is preferred because it requires less content and occupies less vertical height. The extended variant is available in case more content needs to be included.</p>

    {% call components.example(palette='light') %}
        <div class="inline-flex margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">
